Sp(2n,\mathbb{C})
A\in\mathbb{C}^{2n\times 2n}
A^TJA=J
J=\left(\begin{array}{cc} 0& I_n \\ -I_n & 0 \end{array}\right)
I_n
\mathbb{C}^n
x,y\in\mathbb{C}^{2n}
\langle x,y\rangle=x^TJy
Sp(n)
\mathbb{H}^n
p,q\in\mathbb{H}^n
\langle p,q\rangle=\overline{p}^Tq
q=a+b\mathrm{i}+c\mathrm{j}+d\mathrm{k}
\mathbb{H}\rightarrow\mathbb{C}^2
a+b\mathrm{i}+c\mathrm{j}+d\mathrm{k}=(a+b\mathrm{i}) + \mathrm{j}(c-d\mathrm{i})\rightarrow(a+b\mathrm{i},c-d\mathrm{i})
\langle p,p\rangle=\left(\begin{array}{cc} a+b\mathrm{i} & c-d\mathrm{i}\end{array}\right)J\left(\begin{array}{c}a+b\mathrm{i} \\ c-d\mathrm{i}\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc} a+b\mathrm{i} & c-d\mathrm{i}\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}c-d\mathrm{i} \\ -a-b\mathrm{i}\end{array}\right)=0
